  "instructions": [
    "Heat sesame oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add finely chopped shallots and cook until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add Carnaroli rice and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add white wine and cook until absorbed, about 2 minutes.",
    "Add dashi extract and stir to combine.",
    "Add 1 cup of vegetable broth and cook, stirring constantly, until absorbed.",
    "Repeat the process, adding broth in 1-cup increments, until the rice is cooked and creamy, about 20-25 minutes total.",
    "Stir in brown sugar and red wine vinegar.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Transfer to a serving dish and garnish with chopped parsley.",
    "Serve immediately."
